            "description": "ANE is faulted. GPU is READY but MTLDevice.currentAllocatedSize + IOKit residency counters show >80% utilization (e.g., video editing app running).\n\nDecision function skips GPU → drops directly to CPU to prevent UI jank. X-Edge-Device-Status: critical even though GPU is technically available — because the utilization check denied admission."
          },
          "response": [
            {
